A search is under way for a hillwalker who has been reported missing on the Isle of Arran.
David Randle, 73, set off from Glen Rosa campsite, near Brodick, at lunchtime on Thursday.
He is believed to have been intending to walk in an area near Cir Mhor, a Corbett on the west wide of Glen Rosa.
Mr Randle's wife contacted police after he failed to return on Thursday night.
